title: Australian [colour] Diary. No. 11
brief_description: Cinemagazine items: 1. Tony Rasky, caricaturist, gives some impressions of famous sporting personalities - Lew Hoad, Herb Elliot, Peter Thompson. 2. Wellington airport, another ground link in the airways of the sky, opens with a spectacular display of flying, and exhibition of aircraft.
